  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Diagnosis of diabetic retinopathy

               -  macular edema more than 200 micron

               -  vitreous bleeding because of angiography documented NVEs NVDs, based on the
                  definitions of ETDRS

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Prior intraocular injection within 4 months

          -  Core or complete vitrectomy

          -  History of glaucoma or ocular hypertension

          -  Presence of iris neovascularization

          -  Significant media opacity

          -  Monocularity and pregnancy
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
